WEBVTT

00:00:15.949 --> 00:00:17.317
(CHOJI) <i>Human Boulder!</i>

00:00:21.788 --> 00:00:22.556
No way!

00:00:23.056 --> 00:00:23.657
And Cho-Cho...

00:00:25.325 --> 00:00:28.061
that one isn't the only jutsu
that's been passed down through
the Akimichi Clan!

00:00:28.095 --> 00:00:29.630
That's so cool!

00:00:29.663 --> 00:00:31.765
Now watch me very carefully...

00:00:31.798 --> 00:00:35.302
This is a super-secret secret!

00:00:35.335 --> 00:00:41.041
Releasing your chakra all at
once and surpassing the limits
of your physical power...

00:00:41.074 --> 00:00:44.311
Butterfly Mode!

00:00:47.314 --> 00:00:48.315
[grunt]

00:00:56.957 --> 00:00:59.459
Did you see that, Cho-Cho?

00:00:59.493 --> 00:01:01.428
This jutsu will also be-

00:01:01.461 --> 00:01:04.064
[chewing]

00:01:04.097 --> 00:01:07.100
Oh! Tomaru! You are super extra
cool!

00:01:07.434 --> 00:01:11.305
[swooning]

00:01:15.442 --> 00:01:18.579
Our two families are the most
bitter of enemies...

00:01:18.612 --> 00:01:22.749
And that means... for us to fall
in love would be...

00:01:22.783 --> 00:01:25.085
I will never betray you, dear.

00:01:25.118 --> 00:01:28.555
For... as long as you wear this
ring, our love...

00:01:29.957 --> 00:01:31.992
...will shine brightly forever!

00:01:34.561 --> 00:01:37.130
[groaning]

00:01:38.265 --> 00:01:38.398
[eating]

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:41.768
<i>I wonder if we raised her to</i>
<i>be too trendy...</i>

00:01:41.802 --> 00:01:47.541
This is generations-old secret
<i>training, and she's hooked on</i>
<i>chips and a soap opera.</i>

00:01:48.942 --> 00:01:50.110
Oh, Dad...?

00:01:50.143 --> 00:01:50.978
Hm?

00:01:51.812 --> 00:01:54.248
I need you to sign this form.

00:01:54.281 --> 00:01:55.115
Uh, sign it?

00:01:56.383 --> 00:01:58.752
Yup! Sounds like this upcoming
mission is super complicated...

00:01:58.785 --> 00:02:00.921
so they need to do a background
check.

00:02:00.954 --> 00:02:04.892
Hm? Blehhh! You got your
paperwork all greasy! Seriously,
Cho-Cho?!

00:02:04.925 --> 00:02:07.995
Oh, wow Tomaru! You're so cool!

00:02:08.629 --> 00:02:09.997
[chuckle]

